15 SECTION 5.1.(b) There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Alcohol Law
16 Enforcement Division of the Department of Public Safety the sum of seven hundred fifty
17 thousand dollars ($750,000) in recurring funds for the 2026-2027 fiscal year for the purpose of
18 evidence storage and disposal.
19 SECTION 5.1.(c) There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Alcohol Law
20 Enforcement Division of the Department of Public Safety the sum of two million five hundred
21 thousand dollars ($2,500,000) in recurring funds for the 2026-2027 fiscal year for the purpose of
22 hiring up to 37 full-time employees.
23 SECTION 5.1.(d) Subsections (b) and (c) of this section become effective July 1,
24 2026. The remainder of this section is effective when it becomes law.
